				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I read this guide and found it useful.  There is a way to increase the sense headings skill while medding.  My skill was about 5 i think when i made it a hotkey, by left clicking on it and holding which created a button.  Then i pushed F10, for full screen.  I then put it in the lower left corner of the screen in one of the six boxes.  (Always wondered what those where for.)  With in 2 days, always clicking the button while medding, my skill went up to 120.  This is a good thing to do because when your invisible you cant cast true north to tell direction.  Navigating zones is much easier now.  Also i cast sense summoned and glimpse a lot to get my skill up for invisibility.  Good Luck.<BR>
